text: Bill Gulliver (born 28 December 1912) is a Zimbabwean former sports shooter. He competed for Rhodesia in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1912 births Category:Possibly living people Category:British emigrants to Rhodesia Category:Zimbabwean male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Rhodesia Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sheffield
